<D>__{they are.}
<C>__{bellboy}
<D>__{well, who's that?}
<A>__{the clerk looks up from the register and listens.}
<C>__{clerk}
<D>__{i don't know. frank?}
<L>__{interior lounge}
<A>__{judging from the faces, susie's as big a hit in the lounge as she is in the lobby. head thrown back, eyes closed, she sings with abandon, finishing on a long extended note, then swooping down in a dramatic, exhausted bow. there is a split second of silence, then thunderous applause. magic.}
